text: Appingedam is both a small city and a former municipality in the province of Groningen, the Netherlands. In 2019, 11,721 people lived there. Since 2021, it has been part of the new municipality of Eemsdelta. == Other websites == * Official website Category:21st-century disestablishments in the Netherlands Category:Cities in Groningen (province) Category:Former municipalities of Groningen (province) Category:Eemsdelta
